<item>
            <title>[LU-16059] Fix dkms server build installation</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16059</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;linux-zfs-dkms package is passing the wrong paths for spl/zfs causing the dkms build to fail.&lt;br/&gt;
ZFS_VERSION is not calculated correctly.&lt;br/&gt;
splver and zfsver can match against the wrong package.&lt;br/&gt;
lustre-zfs-dkms packages provided kmod-lustre-osd-zfs&#160;but the Provides: is missing.&lt;br/&gt;
lustre-ldiskfs-dkms packages provided kmod-lustre-osd-ldiskfs&#160;but the Provides: is missing.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
